Commands:

# running:

To run locally:

```
ionic serve --nobrowser
```
And navigate to localhost:8100


# Setup
Change Urls (and other env. variables):
can be: dev, prod

eg.
"gulp replace --env localdev"


Or, you can do run:
```
npm setup <environment>
```


# Fixing issues with ionic serve:
if you get issues like the following:

Error: EACCES: permission denied, open '/Users/lewis/.config/configstore/bower-github.json'

This is a permissions issue with npm, try the following:

```
sudo chown -R $USER:$GROUP ~/.npm
sudo chown -R $USER:$GROUP ~/.config
```
